trans-unit.source: Represents one or more <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa um ou mais objetos <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.

trans-unit.source: A Toolset is a combination of a Toolset version (such as "2.0"), a tools path, and an optional set of associated properties.
trans-unit.target: Um Conjunto de Ferramentas é uma combinação de uma versão de Conjunto de Ferramentas (como "2.0"), um caminho de ferramentas e um conjunto opcional de propriedades associadas.

trans-unit.source: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection> allows you to retrieve individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> objects by passing the string value of the tools version corresponding with the desired <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection> permite que você recupere individuais <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> objetos ao passar o valor de cadeia de caracteres da versão ferramentas correspondente com o <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset>.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> object representing the Toolset to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> que representa o Conjunto de Ferramentas a ser adicionado à coleção.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> to this collection.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> especificado a essa coleção.

trans-unit.source: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.Add%2A> replaces any previous value that has the same tools version.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.Add%2A> substitui qualquer valor anterior que tenha a mesma versão de ferramentas.

trans-unit.source: It also notifies the parent <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Engine> of the change.
trans-unit.target: Ele também o notificará o pai <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Engine> da alteração.

trans-unit.source: This method is not supported.
trans-unit.target: Não há suporte para o método.

trans-unit.source: Gets whether the collection contains the referenced <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.
trans-unit.target: Verifica se a coleção contém o <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> referenciado.

trans-unit.source: Required.
trans-unit.target: Necessário.

trans-unit.source: A string value representing the name of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.
trans-unit.target: Um valor de cadeia de caracteres que representa o nome do <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets whether the collection contains a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> with the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> name.
trans-unit.target: Verifica se a coleção tem um <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> com o nome <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> is contained in the collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o item <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> estiver contido na coleção; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Required.
trans-unit.target: Necessário.

trans-unit.source: A string value representing the tools version associated with the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.
trans-unit.target: Um valor de cadeia de caracteres que representa a versão das ferramentas associada ao <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets whether the collection contains a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> with the specified tools version.
trans-unit.target: Verifica se a coleção tem um <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> com a versão das ferramentas especificada.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> is contained in the collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o item <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> estiver contido na coleção; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional que é o destino dos elementos copiados de <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Array" /> deve ter indexação com base em zero.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>Array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero na <c>Matriz</c> em que a cópia começa.

trans-unit.source: Copies the contents of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia os conteúdos do <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> para uma <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional compatível, começando no índice especificado da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the number of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica o número de objetos do <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> no <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: An integer value representing the number of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um valor inteiro que representa o número de <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objetos na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> element in the collection represents a <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> in the project.
trans-unit.target: Cada <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> elemento na coleção representa um <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> no projeto.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um enumerador que itera por meio do <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the entire <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> para todo o <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in Visual Basic) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Esse método permite que o chamador usar o `foreach` instrução de linguagem c# (`for each` no Visual Basic) para iterar individuais <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> objetos no <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection>.

trans-unit.source: Gets whether the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Verifica se a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> é somente leitura.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.IsReadOnly" /> always returns <see langword="false" /> because Toolsets are always writable.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.IsReadOnly" /> sempre retorna <see langword="false" />, porque os Conjuntos de Ferramentas sempre são graváveis.

trans-unit.source: A boolean value indicating whether the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Um valor booliano que indica se o <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> é somente leitura.

trans-unit.source: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.IsReadOnly%2A> always returns `false` because Toolsets are always writable.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.IsReadOnly%2A> sempre retorna `false`, porque os Conjuntos de Ferramentas sempre são graváveis.

trans-unit.source: Required.
trans-unit.target: Necessário.

trans-unit.source: A string value representing the tools version associated with the desired <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.
trans-unit.target: Um valor de cadeia de caracteres que representa a versão das ferramentas associada ao <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> desejado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> associated with the specified tools version.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> associado à versão de ferramentas especificada.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> object representing the toolset that matches the specified <paramref name="toolsVersion" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objeto que representa o conjunto de ferramentas que corresponda a especificado <paramref name="toolsVersion" />.

trans-unit.source: Not supported.
trans-unit.target: Sem suporte.

trans-unit.source: This method is not supported.
trans-unit.target: Não há suporte para o método.

trans-unit.source: Not supported.
trans-unit.target: Sem suporte.

trans-unit.source: Non-generic enumerator for the Toolsets in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Enumerador não genérico para os Conjuntos de Ferramentas nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator for the toolsets.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um enumerador para os conjuntos de ferramentas.

trans-unit.source: Returns the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o enumerador.

trans-unit.source: Gets the names of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />s stored in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os nomes das <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />s nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: An enumeration whose elements represent individual <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objects in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Uma enumeração cujos elementos representam individuais <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objetos nesta coleção.
